Introduction
============

BFilt uses cmake and make to build all its components.

DEPENDANCES
===========

You must install first :

Lapack : It's strongly recomended to compile it with ATLAS.
cpplapack
GSL

INSTALLATION
============

Configure properly the path of differents sources in src/CMakelists.txt
Then type :
cd bin
cmake ../src
make
make install

If doxygene is installed an html documentation is built in doc/.
 
Good luck !
